@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cpvfyg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp((0.37 - 0.08))
    v0 = (0.08 * wp.sin((v0 + 0.23 - v0 + 0.74)))
    v0 = wp.exp((v0 + (v1 + 0.70 / v1 + 0.54)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 0.94 - v0 + 0.45) + (tmp + 0.23 - v0 + 0.01)))
    v1 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.30) / (v2 + 0.49 + tmp + 0.99)) * wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.10)))
    v2 = wp.sin((v2 / wp.abs(v2 + 0.83)))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
